resultDesc: Practical and fact-minded individuals, whose reliability cannot be doubted.
Very dedicated and warm protectors, always ready to defend their loved ones.
Quiet visionaries, often serving as inspiring and tireless idealists.
Imaginative and strategic thinkers, with a plan for everything.
Innovative and practical experimenters, masters of all kinds of tools.
Flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new.
Poetic, kind, and altruistic people, always eager to help a good cause.
Innovative inventors with an unquenchable thirst for knowledge.
Savvy, energetic, and very perceptive people who truly enjoy living on the edge.
Spontaneous, energetic, and enthusiastic people – life is never boring around them.
Enthusiastic, creative, and sociable free spirits, who can always find a reason to smile.
Curious and flexible thinkers who cannot resist an intellectual challenge.
Excellent organizers, unsurpassed at managing things – or people.
Caring, social, community-minded people who are always eager to help.
Inspiring optimists, readily taking action to do what they feel is right.
Bold, imaginative, and strong-willed, always finding a way – or making one.
